<Content>Great Hotel, great location We stayed in the Miramar in December to visit the Christmas market and the location was perfect. We were very impressed with the welcome which included mulled wine and stollen cake.The hotel was spotlessly clean, the room was great and all the staff were friendly and helpful. The included breakfast was ample with lots of choice and really set you up for the day. We will definately be staying at the Hotel Miramar on our next visit to Frankfurt. 
