<Content>Excellent value for money The Miramar is ideally placed for travellers wishing to visit the Christmas markets which are only a minute or so away by foot. Although the rooms are fairly small they are clean and comfortable with good shower rooms. The staff are very pleasant and accommodating and all speak excellent English. Breakfast was also excellent with a good variety of cereals, cold meats, cheese, fruit and bread.Over the weekend we stayed which was very close to Christmas there was always a plate of cookies/cake for guests on reception - a lovely touch.All round, this is a very reasonably priced hotel and the service provided is therefore excellent value. We would stay again. 
