<Author>dangerpre
<Content>Miserable Reservations Service Based on all the positive reviews I had read on this site, I made my reservation directly with this hotel in April 2007, for a stay in October 2007, during a fair and heavy season in Frankfurt. Everything was confirmed via email six months in advance and I was all set for my trip.Two weeks before my trip, the hotel manager sent me an email notifying me that they had accidentally double-booked the hotel for the fair and my reservation had been canceled. Furthermore, they had made a courtesy reservation for me and my family at a nearby hotel (near the train station). I did not want the reservation they made for me in a red light district hotel.Unfortunately, I was unable to find anything reasonable on such last minute in Frankfurt, so I ended up staying at a nearby town, instead of Frankfurt. My advise to anyone looking to book this hotel is to make sure you are not going during heavy season as you too may be accidentally bumped from this hotel. 
